narratives.question_text: What was valuable about the format and content of this class?
comments: Helpful and informative into the world of scenic painting.
It helps designers understand how to budget the scenic painting materials, and improving techniques of scenic painting and get the sense of organizing painting crews and time.
Painting skill, knowing more materials and paints, and get more concept of timing, communicating skill.
